title: The Shannara Chronicles - Season 1 - Episodes 1 thru 9
description:
Season 1
Chosen: Part 1
S1, Ep1
5 Jan. 2016
Chosen: Part 1
Princess Amberle Elessedil is selected to be a member of the Chosen that cares for the most sacred Elven tree, the Ellcrys. However she is given a vision of the Ellcrys dying, which could mean trouble for the Four Lands.
 
Chosen: Part 2
S1, Ep2
5 Jan. 2016
Chosen: Part 2
Wil and Allanon set out to find Amberle while Eventine discovers that there is a spy in the Elven Kingdom.
 
Fury
S1, Ep3
6 Jan. 2016
Fury
On their way back to Arborlon, Wil and Amberle are kidnapped by Eretria and the Rovers. To make matters worse, a Fury demon is hot on their tail.
 
Changeling
S1, Ep4
6 Jan. 2016
Changeling
Wil and Amberle prepare to leave for the Wilderun. However the Changeling continues to murder inside the palace and frames Eretria for the crimes.
 
Reaper
S1, Ep5
26 Jan. 2016
Reaper
The Dagda Mor sends the Reaper after Amberle and Wil as they are taken prisoner, once again, by Cephelo. Allanon trains Bandon. Ander is forced to make a difficult decision.
 
Pykon
S1, Ep6
2 Feb. 2016
Pykon
To throw the demons off their trail, Amberle, Wil, and company take shelter in the abandoned fortress of Pykon. But is it abandoned? The Changeling twists Arion against Allanon.
 
Breakline
S1, Ep7
9 Feb. 2016
Breakline
Having been separated after their fall, Wil meets up with a Winged-Elf named Perk while Amberle and Eretria are on the run from elf hunters. Eventine sends Ander and Arion to kill the Dagda Mor. Allanon tries to heal his wounds.
 
Utopia
S1, Ep8
16 Feb. 2016
Utopia
Wil and Amberle try to rescue Eretria from a human settlement. Ander has mixed feelings about becoming king.
 
Safehold
S1, Ep9
23 Feb. 2016
Safehold
Amberle, Wil, and Eretria work their way through the tunnels of Safehold. Allanon tries to help Bandon fight the Dagda Mor's will. Ander finds his rule tested
